Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,NOW I SLICE EVERYTHING
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I alive?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:02:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought Hyunckel pierced both my hearts,\Nkilling me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That is due to Dark Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You used your Dark Aura power\Nto resurrect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my body even more powerful than before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the secret of the body\NKing Ban has bestowed you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Should you die,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so long as the Dark Aura of King Ban\Nor myself remains, you can be resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And with far greater power than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you were placed under me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra, your body belongs\Nto the almighty King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can no longer choose your own death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should you die, you will return\Nonly to fight on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For your master, King Ban.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gladly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For a silent man of shadows,\Nhe's certainly become quite chatty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,my target!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The power of that core keeps the hot and\Ncold sides of Flazzard's body together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With it now gone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! I can't maintain my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remain together I'll vaporize myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pulverize him\Nso he can't rebuild himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shadow Vizier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban, you've gotta help me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just die like this! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate armour of my Shadow Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would become burning Dark Aura,\Nin other words, a Dark Fire Energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! That would mean\Nbecoming your servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If... If I really merge with that,\NI can beat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be unrivaled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The power! The power is overwhelming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Such unbelievable, extraordinary power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back! I am\Nthe great swordsman of Papunica...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Baduck! Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! They chose\Nthe worst time to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Old timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyadaruko!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My spell's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This body is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:07:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stronger and faster\Nthan I used to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's immune to spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be taking you out later. But first...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to crush this little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back, Maam. He's after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! You don't have the strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some guts, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're begging me to send you\Nto the afterlife with one punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Maam. I can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why,\Nbut I don't feel like I can lose to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't lose to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You do nothing but\Nspout your annoying words!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I can't stand you,\Nyou little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's reading the movements\Nof all those powerful attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And with his eyes closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,By obtaining Air Slash, Dai's completed\Nhis Aban Style Sword Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that super attack\Nis also complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,By super attack, you mean...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai subconsciously understands\Nits destructive power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he knows he can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding! This is impossible!\NI'm supposed to be invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the ultimate body!\NI can't lose to this brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,With this power and this durability...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,if I lose now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look like an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Slice the earth...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Slice the sea...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Slice the air...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And slice everything...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was able to do Air Slash.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know... I know I can slice everything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me, Master Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... This is a true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow! So that's the power\Nof the complete Aban Strash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It rivals Aban, no,\Nit might be even more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You lied to me, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that the ultimate armour?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That was indeed\Nthe ultimate armour of my army.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it merely means your foe's attack\Nwas that much stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Give me another chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystvear--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does such a thing to their own ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did Mystban use Flazzard\Nto test Dai's strength?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks like he's truly\Nthe most dangerous among the Dark Army.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry! To the Princess in the tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:11:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that that monster is dead, the ice\Nof his Forbidden Magic should be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a right bastard, but that was\Na pretty horrible way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we gather the fragments\Nand make a grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's his gravestone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:21.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ABAN STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:26.58,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}TOMAKUGUTSOSHO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't melted at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's started to melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems we were too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Flazzard is dead\Nand his Forbidden Magic is dispelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it appears the Princess doesn't have\Nthe strength to break free of its effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:12:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess! Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your Princess' life ends\Ntomorrow at sundown!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Gira!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's barely melted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case... {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good!\NA normal spell can barely melt it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll have to risk it\Nand try shattering it with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And what if you\Nshatter the Princess, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This contains a Gira spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we charge it with a Begirama spell,\Nmaybe it can fire an even greater heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never charged\Nmore that one spell, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that,\Nyour Magic Bullet Gun might break!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:13:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!\NThis is the Princess' life here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Magic Bullet Gun isn't just some item!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban made it.\NIt's all that's left of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Master said this weapon\Nwas for helping people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he made it for times like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's out of Magic Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Popp! You can't give up!\NYou're the only one who can use Begirama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I really do have a mysterious power\Nlike everyone says...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then let me use that power,\Nnot to fight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but to save a life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To save Leona's life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that mark?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the mystic power within Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not coming from anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's responding to something\Nother than battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's charged!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona... She's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Magic Bullet Gun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's okay, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to you, a person's life was saved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you lot! Are you alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! The food's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A feast! A victory feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Food goes there! Fruits over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Papunica soldiers who were scattered\Nhave begun to gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They heard you rescued the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You really saved us by fixing\Nthe Balloon Ship and coming for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-Princess!\N-The Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!\NThank goodness you're all better!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face was all pale like a King Squid\Nso I was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What, Leona? Have you forgotten me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly! Give me a break, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be the emotional reunion\Nbetween the Princess and her rescuer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to read the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You have all fought bravely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially Dai and the other\NDisciples of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No words can express our gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was right to send\NMaster Aban as a Hero's Tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:17:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The King of Papunica was killed\Nduring the Dark Army's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, the Princess has united\Nthe people and continued to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Dai, is that swordsman also\Na Disciple of Aban?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, of course he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I should thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona, there's something\NI have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Leona, he's, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Undead Legion Commander\Nof the Dark Army, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Undead Legion Commander?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!\NHe's not in the Dark Army anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! He's awakened to his duty\Nas a Disciple of Aban and helped us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how I may have atoned for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact remains that, as Undead Legion\NCommander, I destroyed this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona, I ask that you judge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can cut me down now if be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was blessed to be saved\Nand to lend my strength to Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can die fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,as you wish, I Leona, Princess of Papunica,\Nshall pass judgment upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You will spend the rest of your life,\Nserving your duty as a Disciple of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You will risk your life to fight\Nfor friendship, justice, and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And you must never disparage yourself\Nor become lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and cease from moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all. Is that understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us all move forward together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's more capable than she looks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Papunica just might rise from the ashes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We were looking for you.\NWhat are you doing drinking alone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster shouldn't\Nbe drinking with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous! A hero\Nis a hero no matter their race!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers to the Princess' savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the most delicious drink\NI've ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentor! I can't breath here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:20:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Princess. I didn't know\NUncle Matorif would cut loose like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be formal.\NYou can call me Leona, not "Princess."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I'll start\Ncalling you "Ms. Maam."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel! What's wrong!?\NWhere are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We were going to leave unannounced...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to Sovereign Rock Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sovereign Rock Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The fortress of the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's north of Papunica,\Ndeep in the mountains of Guildmain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine and I are going\Nto check their movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we all go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be easier with just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please trust us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a wonderful time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Give my regards to Dai\Nand the people of Papunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet again, Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This man is a monster!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even Carl Kingdom,\Nwith its dozens of powerful knights,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is on the brink of ruin\Nafter only five days!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy Dai seems quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He managed to fight off\Nthe whole Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a strange boy\Nwith a mysterious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When this mark shines on his forehead,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,he exhibits this amazing power...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A mark?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera, does that mark\Nresemble the face of a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that you mention it,\Nit does seem similar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Hadorra!\NI know what you're up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:25.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:32.91,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:36.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.63,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:52.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:57.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:01.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:08.11,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:13.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:19.25,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai and friends defeated Flazzard\Nand rescued Leona.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As they prepare for their next battle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}her broken Magic Bullet Gun\Nleads Maam to a decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Kilban the Reaper\Nappears before Dark Commander Hadorra.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Sovereign Rock Castle, the fortress of\Nthe Dark Army, shows its true form.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:23:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Maam's Decision"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:24:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
